{"tid":1007661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社工幫手呃綜援","createTime":"2019-02-04T02:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T14:46:28.000Z","uid":18739,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d9a78bffdacc6e59438fbafef5a8b502195dad1","tid":1007661,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NRGte4t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNRGte4t.png&h=adde2203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/daily/article/20190204/20605713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F20605713&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=84b11f34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F20605713&h=490942f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/daily/article/20190204/20605713</a><br />\n<br />\n領綜援、爭公屋不是他們的錯，誰叫特區政府喜歡派錢，有食唔食罪大惡極。<br />\n<br />\n但一個香港阿婆和兩個新移民長者，怎懂得先把物業甩掉來騙取福利呢？答案令我難以置信：給他們仙人指路的，是社工。<br />\n<br />\n我已要求朋友舉報，儘管我知道很難成功。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n社工幫手呃綜援，有幾難以置信呀"},{"pid":"93d4b0a67d9ee51eba70ad5604a35ace4d673a49","tid":1007661,"uid":191815,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:31:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">包括上公屋，班社工本身好多政治聯繋，如果唔係邊有咁得咁多新移民特快上樓</span>"},{"pid":"9317c0e568131c0a60e42c7414cbc8d92e470321","tid":1007661,"uid":242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"捉佢地出黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\"