,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"班狗官真係好仆街🤦🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"2c6a091d8d909c6fa16cf090a9186498248952e0","tid":1007661,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"to be fair<br />\n而家新移民要申請福利使撚社工<br />\nd工賊會淫賤聯乜柒同鄉大把人幫佢搞啦<br />\n社工反而有專業守則規管<br />\n教人虛報隨時工都冇埋"},{"pid":"d0f98a3f4a1957320982f36475b6d4199b113084","tid":1007661,"uid":233371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cb9211db782124a9644ebc8d7ca2150f9b0974e","tid":1007661,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NRGte4t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNRGte4t.png&h=adde2203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/daily/article/20190204/20605713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F20605713&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=84b11f34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F20605713&h=490942f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/daily/article/20190204/20605713</a><br />\n<br />\n領綜援、爭公屋不是他們的錯，誰叫特區政府喜歡派錢，有食唔食罪大惡極。<br />\n<br />\n但一個香港阿婆和兩個新移民長者，<span style=\"color: red;\">怎懂得先把物業甩掉來騙取福利呢？</span>答案令我難以置信：給他們仙人指路的，是社工。<br />\n<br />\n我已要求朋友舉報，儘管我知道很難成功。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n社工幫手呃綜援，有幾難以置信呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果個社工話佢知有非自住物業不能申請<br />\n咁只係政策解釋,冇錯喎<br />\n如果個社工話甩左(如變賣)後可以申請綜援<br />\n咁就係陰9個新移民<br />\n因為變賣物業都要報資產<br />\n<br />\n果真如此,咁做乜仲on99舉報社工<br />\n直接督個騙綜援既大陸人啦"},{"pid":"f27b7077554beffd6e7349e5cafd46f5ad3b4ca2","tid":1007661,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0f98a3f4a1957320982f36475b6d4199b113084","tid":1007661,"uid":233371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2c6a091d8d909c6fa16cf090a9186498248952e0","tid":1007661,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"to be fair<br />\n而家新移民要申請福利使撚社工<br />\nd工賊會淫賤聯乜柒同鄉大把人幫佢搞啦<br />\n社工反而有專業守則規管<br />\n教人虛報隨時工都冇埋"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:25:16.000Z","msg":"提點咪即係教囉<br />\n如打工心態做乜撚要冒險<br />\n違反社工守則教人犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邊d人最鍾意好熱心幫人填表拿福利<br />\n騙地址騙資料拿聯繫<br />\n咪就係建制狗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025fc0d168d8700d7cd0f65dece2314fbaa6d611","tid":1007661,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8739288fc6732c640b0f9aee15d85a77ad90be45","tid":1007661,"uid":72058,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:49:49.000Z","msg":"恩卹安置一定要經社署做<br />\n唔係篤下個鼻話社工轉介就得架"},{"pid":"676fddcc6d99a2fd7a61e14dc9105f2ca286d357","tid":1007661,"uid":242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37315c868f60febf349b78f05cfe5193356bc914","tid":1007661,"uid":18739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7ee54b40fa4adfae13c1857e7138f0c6c4366b4a","tid":1007661,"uid":242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9317c0e568131c0a60e42c7414cbc8d92e470321","tid":1007661,"uid":242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"捉佢地出黎打<im