f-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F20605713&h=490942f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/daily/article/20190204/20605713</a><br />\n<br />\n領綜援、爭公屋不是他們的錯，誰叫特區政府喜歡派錢，有食唔食罪大惡極。<br />\n<br />\n但一個香港阿婆和兩個新移民長者，<span style=\"color: red;\">怎懂得先把物業甩掉來騙取福利呢？</span>答案令我難以置信：給他們仙人指路的，是社工。<br />\n<br />\n我已要求朋友舉報，儘管我知道很難成功。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n社工幫手呃綜援，有幾難以置信呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果個社工話佢知有非自住物業不能申請<br />\n咁只係政策解釋,冇錯喎<br />\n如果個社工話甩左(如變賣)後可以申請綜援<br />\n咁就係陰9個新移民<br />\n因為變賣物業都要報資產<br />\n<br />\n果真如此,咁做乜仲on99舉報社工<br />\n直接督個騙綜援既大陸人啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T17:58:13.000Z","msg":"搵律師改左層樓唔係自己名咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  邊度話我有樓？睇過！"},{"pid":"6e4d77d5d35dd36ba449610ca3f36b4eeca7f331","tid":1007661,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ab5ba124327a3f5b146c51e0f3b89d73718b97e","tid":1007661,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"025fc0d168d8700d7cd0f65dece2314fbaa6d611","tid":1007661,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8739288fc6732c640b0f9aee15d85a77ad90be45","tid":1007661,"uid":72058,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:49:49.000Z","msg":"恩卹安置一定要經社署做<br />\n唔係篤下個鼻話社工轉介就得架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T18:11:1